platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Grab a seat with Apple Pay

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Fandango makes every movie night better by giving you instant access to tickets and showtimes for thousands of theaters. Browse by theater name or film title, or discover new and upcoming releases you might have missed in the curated Spotlight view. Save a list of your favorite films and venues, then purchase tickets with just a few taps. More than a mobile box office, Fandango is packed with perks for movie lovers, including trailers, clips, and quick access to showings about to start.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Check out what's showing and go see a movie.
